4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp designed to equip students with essential skills in technologies like JavaScript and Python over a span of 18 weeks. The program emphasizes building websites, algorithm scripting, and creating applications using front-end libraries and APIs. Classes consist of small groups with a 1:7 instructor-to-student ratio, ensuring personalized attention. There are no prerequisites required for enrollment, and learners can choose to study in either English or Spanish. Participants will complete the course by developing and presenting a final project. More information is available at [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer). stop